{"id":482,"category_slug":"english-conversations","category_name":"Conversations","position":84,"title":"84. A Date (2)","subtitle":"","level":"B1","parts":15,"url":"https://dailydictation.com/exercises/english-conversations/84-a-date-2.482/listen-and-type","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/84-a-date-2-2022-03-07-21-32-13/0-84-a-date-2.mp3","transcript":"Hello?\nSandy? Is that you?\nYes, uh-huh. Who's this?\nIt's Gill.\nGill? Gill who?\nWhat do you mean, \"Gill who?\" Gill Dixon, of course.\nOh, Gill, I'm sorry.\nYes. We had a date last night.\nWhere were you? I waited for one hour.\nOh, I'm sorry, Gill. I couldn't come.\nCouldn't come! Why not?\nWell, I had to pack my stuff for my trip.\nWhy didn't you call me?\nI wanted to call you, but... uh... I couldn't remember your phone number.\nAnd now I'm going to forget yours!","youtube_video_id":"","details_cached_at":"2026-06-15T20:49:05","challenges":[{"position":1,"content":"Hello?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/84-a-date-2-2022-03-07-21-32-13/1.mp3","time_start":4.12,"time_end":5.01},{"position":2,"content":"Sandy? Is that you?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/84-a-date-2-2022-03-07-21-32-13/2.mp3","time_start":5.01,"time_end":6.84},{"position":3,"content":"Yes, uh-huh. Who's this?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/84-a-date-2-2022-03-07-21-32-13/3.mp3","time_start":6.84,"time_end":8.7},{"position":4,"content":"It's Gill.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/84-a-date-2-2022-03-07-21-32-13/4.mp3","time_start":8.7,"time_end":9.56},{"position":5,"content":"Gill? Gill who?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/84-a-date-2-2022-03-07-21-32-13/5.mp3","time_start":9.56,"time_end":11.09},{"position":6,"content":"What do you mean, \"Gill who?\" Gill Dixon, of course.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/84-a-date-2-2022-03-07-21-32-13/6.mp3","time_start":11.25,"time_end":14.31},{"position":7,"content":"Oh, Gill, I'm sorry.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/84-a-date-2-2022-03-07-21-32-13/7.mp3","time_start":14.31,"time_end":16.82},{"position":8,"content":"Yes. We had a date last night.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/84-a-date-2-2022-03-07-21-32-13/8.mp3","time_start":16.82,"time_end":18.85},{"position":9,"content":"Where were you? I waited for one hour.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/84-a-date-2-2022-03-07-21-32-13/9.mp3","time_start":18.96,"time_end":21.65},{"position":10,"content":"Oh, I'm sorry, Gill. I couldn't come.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/84-a-date-2-2022-03-07-21-32-13/10.mp3","time_start":21.65,"time_end":24.04},{"position":11,"content":"Couldn't come! Why not?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/84-a-date-2-2022-03-07-21-32-13/11.mp3","time_start":24.04,"time_end":26.04},{"position":12,"content":"Well, I had to pack my stuff for my trip.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/84-a-date-2-2022-03-07-21-32-13/12.mp3","time_start":26.04,"time_end":28.36},{"position":13,"content":"Why didn't you call me?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/84-a-date-2-2022-03-07-21-32-13/13.mp3","time_start":28.56,"time_end":30.04},{"position":14,"content":"I wanted to call you, but... uh... I couldn't remember your phone number.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/84-a-date-2-2022-03-07-21-32-13/14.mp3","time_start":30.04,"time_end":34.36},{"position":15,"content":"And now I'm going to forget yours!","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/84-a-date-2-2022-03-07-21-32-13/15.mp3","time_start":34.55,"time_end":36.92}]}